Package com.ibm.collaboration.realtime.gateway.event

Interface Summary
Event The root interface in the gateway event hierachy
EventStatus The root interface in the gateway event status hierarchy.
ImEvent This is an interface to retrieve or modify the text of the instant messages exchanged between chat participants.
PresenceEvent This is an interface to retrieve information about the Presence Event
SessionEvent This interface provides the methods to retrieve the information about the IM session.
SessionEventStatus SessionEventStatus holds the details session event status details: session and request IDs that matches the request, request status (error code), reason, originating user.
 

Class Summary
EventStatusFactory EventStatusFactory is used to create instances of the event status object.
